ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    Mapper.RequiredValues && Mapper.DisplayMode = DisplayMode.Edit && IsEmpty(Items),
    Mapper.Style.Palette.Warning,
    Color.Transparent
)

Self.PaddingTop + Self.PaddingBottom + 42 + ctnControls_Mapper.Height + 10 + If(
    CountRows(Items) < 3,
    96,
    CountRows(Items) * 32
)
